    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliable performance. The engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts as expected, making it a dependable choice for daily commuting or longer trips. While the exterior and interior show minor signs of regular use, such as small surface scratches and light wear on the upholstery, the overall appearance remains clean and well-kept. All essential features are fully functional, and it offers a comfortable driving experience with no major mechanical issues to report.",
