      "description": "Hey there! I'm honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car is in absolutely flawless condition\u2014it truly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it garage-kept and spotless. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. If you're looking for perfection, you've found it! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
