    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Presenting a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) finished in Titanium Silver over Black Nappa leather. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. Mechanically flawless, the dual-VANOS system has been professionally overhauled, and the rear subframe\u2014a known weak point\u2014has been structurally reinforced for longevity. The chassis remains taut with original bushings and Bilstein B6 dampers, while the limited-slip M-differential provides exceptional torque vectoring. This is a true collector-quality specimen with zero oxidation, original VIN tags on all panels, and a comprehensive service log. A pure, analog driving experience that represents the pinnacle of M-division engineering.",
